lement of the personal name Mai Zhu Chu (買朱鉏), style name of an official who lived during the Spring and Autumn period (770–476  BC ). (iv) it has also been traced back to other ethnic groups in northern China."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mac Sulleabhainn was born about 0925, in Ireland. She had at least 1 son with Lorcan MacSúilleabháinn."},"et":{"about 0925–":"umbes 0925–Surnud","0914–Male":"0914–Surnud","0954–Male":"0954–Surnud","0925–Female":"0925–Surnud","about 0925":"umbes 0925","954":"0954","0925":"0925","0914":"0914","0954":"0954","Ireland":"Iirimaa"},"fi":{"about 0925–":"noin 0925–Kuollut","0914–Male":"0914–Kuollut","0954–Male":"0954–Kuollut","0925–Female":"0925–Kuollut","about 0925":"noin 0925","954":"0954","0925":"0925","0914":"0914","0954":"0954","Ireland":"Irlanti"},"fr":{"about 0925–":"environ 0925–Décédée","0914–Male":"0914–Décédé","0954–Male":"0954–Décédé","0925–Female":"0925–Décédée","about 0925":"environ 0925","954":"0954","0925":"0925","0914":"0914","0954":"0954","Ireland":"Irlande","lifeSummary":"Mac Sulleabhainn est née environ 0925, à Irlande. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Lorcan MacSúilleabháinn."},"de":{"about 0925–":"um 0925–Verstorben","0914–Male":"0914–Verstorben","0954–Male":"0954–Verstorben","0925–Female":"0925–Verstorben","about 0925":"um 0925","954":"0954","0925":"0925","0914":"0914","0954":"0954","Ireland":"Irland","lifeSummary":"Mac Sulleabhainn wurde um 0925 in Irland geboren. Sie hatte mit Lorcan MacSúilleabháinn mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 0925–":"about 0925–Desede","0914–Male":"0914–Desede","0954–Male":"0954–Desede","0925–Female":"0925–Desede","about 0925":"about 0925","954":"0954","0925":"0925","0914":"0914","0954":"0954","Ireland":"Irlande"},"hu":{"about 0925–":"0925 körül–elhunyt","0914–Male":"0914–elhunyt","0954–Male":"0954–elhunyt","0925–Female":"0925–elhunyt","about 0925":"0925 körül","954":"0954","0925":"0925","0914":"0914","0954":"0954","Ireland":"Írország"},"id":{"about 0925–":"sekitar 0925–Telah Meninggal","0914–Male":"